==开发==
在{{tsl|en|E3 2014|}}上，育碧高管托尼·凯（{{Lang|en|Tony Key}}）称他们对《看门狗》的销量非常满意，该系列会得到长期开发<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/e3-2014-ubisoft-says-watch-dogs-is-a-franchise-now/1100-6420372/|title=E3 2014: Ubisoft Says Watch Dogs Is a Franchise -- "Now We Figure Out What To Do Next"|accessdate=2016-06-09|date=2014-09-22|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date=2014-10-08|archive-url=https://archive.is/20141008230845/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/e3-2014-ubisoft-says-watch-dogs-is-a-franchise-now/1100-6420372/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据创意总监乔纳森·莫林所述，首款游戏的主要目标是建立起《看门狗》这一品牌。莫林说他们打算在续作大胆创新，而不去制作一个將前作改良的版本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamestm.co.uk/discuss/watch-dogs-2-will-carry-on-taking-risks-says-ubisoft/|title=Watch Dogs 2 will “carry on taking risks” says Ubisoft|accessdate=2016-06-09|work=[[GamesTM|GamesTM]]|archive-date=2015-01-17|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150117030705/http://www.gamestm.co.uk/discuss/watch-dogs-2-will-carry-on-taking-risks-says-ubisoft/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为了提高游戏素质，莫林和他的团队看了前作的评论，访问了{{tsl|en|NeoGAF|}}等论坛，研究了玩家的反馈。他们的优先任务包括建立一个“可信”的环境、给予玩家更多自由、增强驾驶系统让它不再感觉那么像“[[模擬|模拟]]”以及引入新的主角，其个性与前作主角艾登·皮尔斯（{{Lang|en|Aiden Pierce}}）完全不同<ref name="GSpot2" />。

《[[看門狗_(遊戲)|看门狗]]》发行后，关于续作的传言就一直不断传出。发行商育碧2016年2月和5月的财务报告证实了续作的存在<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/watch-dogs-2-confirmed-due-out-before-april-2017/|title=Watch Dogs 2 confirmed, due out before April 2017|accessdate=2016-06-09|date=2016-02-12|last=Chalk|first=Andy|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|archive-date=2016-06-09|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160609140433/http://www.pcgamer.com/watch-dogs-2-confirmed-due-out-before-april-2017/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-05-04-it-looks-like-a-mocap-actor-has-revealed-watch-dogs-2s-new-protagonist|title=It looks like a mocap actor has revealed Watch Dogs 2's new protagonist|accessdate=2016-06-09|date=2016-05-04|last=Phillips|first=Tom|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|archive-date=2016-06-09|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160609140827/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-05-04-it-looks-like-a-mocap-actor-has-revealed-watch-dogs-2s-new-protagonist|dead-url=no}}</ref>。公司证实游戏将参加2016年的E3大展，并在6月8日发布了一个近20分钟的在线演示视频<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/6/8/11884694/watch-dogs-2-live-stream|title=Here's the Watch Dogs 2 world premiere|accessdate=2016-06-09|date=2016-06-08|last=Grant|first=Christopher|work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|archive-date=2016-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609032550/http://www.polygon.com/2016/6/8/11884694/watch-dogs-2-live-stream|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

